=9CNO DISSENT.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0<=
/p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">Of course, the mood in Washingt=
on during a shutdown week has a tendency to change every few hours. Perhaps
