</strong>=E2=80=99s efforts to strangle the federal government.</p><p style=
=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;
margin-bottom:0px;">But Trump and Johnson are making a big and risky bet th=
at they can keep their conference in line, just as they did during Johnson=
=E2=80=99s speaker vote on January 3, and again two weeks ago, when House R=
epublicans narrowly passed their budget framework. The dynamics here are si=
milar: Once again, <strong>Thomas Massie</strong> is a renegade. But as my =
partner <strong>Leigh Ann Caldwell</strong> reported the other week, Trump =
wields a <em>brutal </em>whipping operation, and isn=E2=80=99t
afraid to personally <a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI=
