bend holdouts to his will. =E2=80=9CIt shocked us when he was able to get t=
he speaker vote in one [round of voting], and turn it around,=E2=80=9D a Ho=
use Democratic chief of staff told me, espousing the view that Trump has la=
rgely subordinated even the Freedom Caucus to his will.=C2=A0</p><p style=
=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;">Trump and=
 Johnson are so confident, in fact, that they=E2=80=99re not even attemptin=
