n</em>, in an interview that quickly made the rounds on the Hill. =E2=80=9C=
Right now, I=E2=80=99m a no,=E2=80=9D he told CBS=E2=80=99s <strong>Margare=
t Brennan</strong>. =E2=80=9CI mean, there=E2=80=99s been no outreach on a =
bipartisan basis.=E2=80=9D Suozzi is <em>exactly</em> the kind of Democrat =
who,
in a previous era, would be participating in aisle-crossing back-channel ta=
lks among friendly members: He=E2=80=99s from a Trumpy Long Island district=
, and he has a history of defying party leadership. If Johnson isn=E2=80=99=
t courting Suozzi, the thinking goes, he=E2=80=99s not reaching out to anyo=
ne.</p></div>
